snippet.title: A VERY PRO POSTAL CHRISTMAS
snippet.description:
Paradise is a distant memory, but does this sleepy, snow-capped town hold even darker secrets?

Patrons see episodes early:
https://www.patreon.com/civvie11
Twitter: https://twitter.com/civvie11
Join the Dungeon Discord: https://discord.gg/CEBKKJS

Mods used:
ALCRD's Weapons Pack
P2M@DMods

Music Used:
Lee Jackson - "God Rest Ye Deadly Gentlemen" from Rise of the Triad
Jingle Punks - "Silent Night," "O, Christmas Tree," 
Bobby Prince - "Nobody Told Me About Id"
Sir Cubworth - "Monster at the Door," "Sea Ritual"

#FreeCivvie #Christmas #ProPostal
